"URL</span>을 눌러 위에 붙여넣으세요."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/pingboard/channel_form.html
msgid ""
"Easiest: create an <span class=\"text-ink\">Incoming Webhook</span> at "
"api.slack.com/apps → your app → <span class=\"text-ink\">Incoming "
"Webhooks</span>, and paste the <span class=\"font-"
"mono\">hooks.slack.com/services/…</span> URL. For DMs to pilots, set a bot "
"token (<span class=\"font-mono\">PINGBOARD_SLACK_BOT_TOKEN</span>) in the "
"environment instead and give a channel id."
msgstr ""
"가장 쉬운 방법: api.slack.com/apps → 해당 앱 → <span class=\"text-ink\">Incoming "
"Webhooks</span>에서 <span class=\"text-ink\">Incoming Webhook</span>을 만들고 "
"<span class=\"font-mono\">hooks.slack.com/services/…</span> URL을 붙여넣으세요. "
"파일럿에게 DM을 보내려면 대신 환경 변수에 봇 토큰(<span class=\"font-"
"mono\">PINGBOARD_SLACK_BOT_TOKEN</span>)을 설정하고 채널 id를 입력하세요."

