msgid "Qty"
msgstr "수량"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/mandatory_ships.html
msgid "Add a mandatory ship"
msgstr "필수 함선 추가"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/mandatory_ships.html
msgid "Add ship"
msgstr "함선 추가"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/responsibilities.html
msgid "Readiness · Officer responsibilities"
msgstr "준비 태세 · 오피서 책임"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/responsibilities.html
msgid ""
"Map each dimension to an owner desk, and assign members to those desks. A "
"generated task routes to the first member on its desk; an unmapped dimension"
" leaves its tasks in the open claimable pool."
msgstr ""
"각 영역을 담당 데스크에 매핑하고, 해당 데스크에 멤버를 배정하세요. 생성된 작업은 데스크의 첫 번째 멤버에게 라우팅됩니다. 매핑되지 "
"않은 영역의 작업은 누구나 가져갈 수 있는 공개 풀에 남습니다."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/responsibilities.html
msgid "Owner desks"
msgstr "담당 데스크"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/responsibilities.html
msgid "Desk label"
msgstr "데스크 라벨"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/responsibilities.html
msgid "Assigned members"
msgstr "배정된 멤버"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/responsibilities.html
msgid "(ctrl/⌘-click for several; first = auto-assignee)"
msgstr "(여러 명은 ctrl/⌘-클릭, 첫 번째 = 자동 담당자)"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/responsibilities.html
msgid "Dimension → owner desk"
msgstr "영역 → 담당 데스크"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/responsibilities.html
msgid "— unassigned (claimable) —"
msgstr "— 미배정 (누구나 가져갈 수 있음) —"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/responsibilities.html
msgid ""
"Restores the desk labels and dimension mapping to the shipped defaults "
"(clears member assignments)."
msgstr "데스크 라벨과 영역 매핑을 출고 기본값으로 되돌립니다 (멤버 배정은 지워집니다)."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/srp.html
msgid ""
"The bounds the <span class=\"text-cyan\">SRP Health</span> dimension scores "
"its backlog, wait-time and oldest-claim KPIs against. Leave a field blank to"
" keep its current value."
msgstr ""
"<span class=\"text-cyan\">SRP 건전성</span> 영역이 백로그, 대기 시간, 최장기 미처리 청구 KPI를 채점할"
" 때 기준으로 삼는 한계값입니다. 현재 값을 유지하려면 항목을 비워 두세요."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/srp.html
msgid "Restores every SRP threshold to the shipped defaults."
msgstr "모든 SRP 임계값을 출고 기본값으로 되돌립니다."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/staging.html
msgid ""
"The system your fleet stages out of. The <span class=\"text-cyan\">Asset Staging</span>\n"
"    dimension scores the share of member-owned doctrine hulls actually sitting here (resolved from each pilot's asset list).\n"
"    <span class=\"text-ink\">Until you set a staging system the dimension is unavailable</span> — it stays disabled until one is chosen."
msgstr ""
"함대가 출격 거점으로 삼는 성계입니다. <span class=\"text-cyan\">자산 스테이징</span> 영역은 멤버가 보유한 "
"doctrine 선체 중 실제로 이곳에 있는 비율을 채점합니다 (각 파일럿의 자산 목록으로 확인). <span class=\"text-"
"ink\">스테이징 시스템을 설정하기 전까지 이 영역은 사용할 수 없습니다</span> — 하나를 선택할 때까지 비활성화됨 상태로 "
"남습니다."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/staging.html
msgid "Current staging"
msgstr "현재 스테이징"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/staging.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Asset Staging is <span class=\"text-cyan\">enabled</span> in the index — "
"adjust on <a href=\"%(dimensions_url)s\" class=\"text-gold "
"hover:underline\">Dimensions &amp; weights</a>."
msgstr ""
"자산 스테이징이 지수에 <span class=\"text-cyan\">활성화</span>되어 있습니다 — <a "
"href=\"%(dimensions_url)s\" class=\"text-gold hover:underline\">차원 &amp; "
"가중치</a>에서 조정하세요."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/staging.html
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Scoring now, but <span class=\"text-ink\">not yet in the index</span> — "
"enable it on <a href=\"%(dimensions_url)s\" class=\"text-gold "
"hover:underline\">Dimensions &amp; weights</a>."
msgstr ""
"현재 채점 중이지만 <span class=\"text-ink\">아직 지수에는 반영되지 않았습니다</span> — <a "
"href=\"%(dimensions_url)s\" class=\"text-gold hover:underline\">차원 &amp; "
"가중치</a>에서 활성화하세요."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/staging.html
msgid ""
"No staging system set — choose one below. Until you do, the Asset Staging "
"dimension stays unavailable."
msgstr ""
"스테이징 시스템이 설정되지 않았습니다 — 아래에서 선택하세요. 선택하기 전까지 자산 스테이징 영역은 사용할 수 없는 상태로 남습니다."

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/staging.html
msgid "Change staging system"
msgstr "스테이징 시스템 변경"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/staging.html
msgid "Set staging system"
msgstr "스테이징 시스템 설정"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/staging.html
msgid "Search for a system, e.g. Jita…"
msgstr "성계 검색, 예: Jita…"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/staging.html
msgid "Save staging system"
msgstr "스테이징 시스템 저장"

#: templates/admin_audit/console/readiness/strategic_roles.html
msgid ""
"Desired headcount per strategic role. The <span class=\"text-cyan\">Fleet "
"Composition</span>, <span class=\"text-cyan\">Strategic Assets</span> and "
"<span class=\"text-cyan\">Leadership</span> dimensions score qualified "
"pilots against these targets. For <span class=\"text-ink\">By skills</span> "
"detection, set params like <code class=\"text-faint\">{\"skills\": "
"{\"3300\": 5}}</code> (skill type id → level); <span class=\"text-"
"ink\">manual</span>/<span class=\"text-ink\">asset</span> targets are "
"tracked but not auto-counted yet."
msgstr ""
"전략 역할별 목표 인원수입니다. <span class=\"text-cyan\">함대 편성</span>, <span "
